MTN has announced its new 80GB Mega Deal, which comprises 80GB of mobile data priced at R299 per month for a period of 24 months. Customers who sign up, or upgrade on the My MTNChoice 10GB data plan, will receive 80GB data (40GB Anytime + 40GB Night Express) every month for 24 months. The deal is available from 1 August – 31 August 2019. In the first month of the contract, customers will also receive an additional 20GB promotional data and MTN’s 14GB Entertainment Pass. Entertainment Pass includes an allocation of mobile data which can only be used for selected social and media content. Customers have an option of taking the offer as a SIM only, or with a device at an additional cost. For an extra R30 per month, customers can get a ShareLink Mi-Fi Router as part of the 80GB data deal. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-315097" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/MTN-Mega-Deals.png" alt="MTN Mega Deals" width="640" height="814" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/MTN-Mega-Deals.png 551w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/MTN-Mega-Deals-314x400.png 314w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/MTN-Mega-Deals-338x430.png 338w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" />